AmortizationScheduleList is a List
    title is "AmortizationSchedule"
    suppress sub-totals
    disable select in webui
    Display Fields
        InvoiceDate
        PaymentAmount
            total
        StraightLine
            total
        DerivedAccruedRent
            column visible when (HasAccruedRent)
        DerivedAccumulatedAccruedRent
            column visible when (HasAccruedRent)
        TotalStraightLineIDCAmount
            label is "DeferredIDC"
            total
            column visible when (HasIDC)
        TotalStraightLineIncentiveAmount
            label is "DeferredIncentiveCost"
            total
            column visible when (HasIncentives)
    open action is restricted
    restrict action Create
    restrict action Update
    restrict action Delete
    restrict action RecurringBilling
    restrict action CreateInvoices
    restrict action PeriodProcessing
    Actions
        action is search
            label is "_"
